==German==
===Etymology===
probably from the similarity of the face to minced meat, ''Hack(fleisch)'', combined with ''Fresse'', a derisive term for "mouth".
===Noun===
'''Hackfresse''' ''f''
# very derisive term for a person that is perceived as ugly, comparable to [[shitface]]
#:''schau dir mal die Hackfresse an''
